metadata.name: SINKHOLES Token
metadata.description:
SINKHOLES Token holders receive airdrops and access to reserved sales.

Sinkholes fascinate me as this intersection between geology and biology, between slow change and frenetic adapting. Earth gives way. The remaining void exposes millennia of natural history shown through the fossil record. And in that void flora and fauna race to fill the gaps, whether that space is wet or dry.
